desc: Wheat State Wagyu is dedicated to providing Kansans with the highest quality American Wagyu beef. Raised in Kansas, with generations of quality breeding, our beef is unmatched in richness and flavor. If you’re seeking the best beef on the planet, you know Kansas competes in every regard, ensuring our Wagyu is the best
